  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, smoky paprika, garlic powder, salt, and pepper.",
    "3. Add pork cubes to the bowl and toss to coat with marinade.",
    "4. Thread pork cubes, onion, bell pepper, and pickled peppers onto skewers.",
    "5. Brush skewers with remaining marinade.",
    "6. Grill skewers for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally, or until pork is cooked through.",
    "7. Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley and a side of bread."
